    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0054', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:197'>欽定四庫全書　　　　　經部二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='197:214'>　洪範正論　　　　　　　書𩔖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='214:220'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='220:239'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案洪範正論五卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='239:262'>　　　國朝胡渭撰渭有禹貢錐指已著録此書大㫖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='262:285'>　　　　以禹之治水本於九疇故首言鯀堙洪水繼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='285:308'>　　　　言禹乃嗣興終言天乃錫禹則洪範為體而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='308:331'>　　　　禹貢為用互相推闡其義乃彰然大㫖主於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='331:357'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0054', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='357:381'>　　　　𤼵明奉若天道之理非鄭樵禹貢洪範相為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='381:404'>　　　　表裏之說惟以九州次序分配五行者比也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='404:427'>　　　　其辨証前人之説如謂漢人專取灾祥推衍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='427:450'>　　　　五行穿鑿附㑹事同讖緯其病一洛書本文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='450:473'>　　　　即五行五事至五福六極十二字惟敬用農</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='473:496'>　　　　用十八字為禹所加與危微精一之心法同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='496:519'>　　　　㫖初一次二至次九不過是次第名色亦非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='519:542'>　　　　龜文所有龜之有文如木石之文又如魯夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='542:568'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0054', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='568:592'>　　　　人公子友有文在手之𩔖宋儒創為黒白之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='592:615'>　　　　㸃方圓之體九十之位變書而為圖以至九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='615:638'>　　　　數十數劉牧蔡季通紛紜更定其病二又洪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='638:661'>　　　　範原無錯簡而王栢胡一桂等任意改竄其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='661:684'>　　　　病三皆切中舊說之失葢渭經術湛深學問</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='684:707'>　　　　有根柢故所論一軌於理漢儒附㑹之談宋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='707:730'>　　　　儒變亂之論能一掃而廓清之云乾隆四十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='730:743'>　　　　四年八月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='743:769'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0054', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='769:801'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='801:827'>　　　　　　　　　　總　校　官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸　費　墀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='847:873'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0054', 'WYG', '000-3a' );" name="000-3a" class="pb">[000-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='873:877'>原序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='877:900'>洪範一書如日月之麗天有目者所共覩而問有晦肓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='900:923'>否塞者則先儒之曲説為之害也五亊本於五行庶徴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='923:947'>本於五事不過以雨𤾉燠寒風之時不時驗貌言視聽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='947:970'>思之敬不敬而漢儒五行傳專主災異其所言貌之不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='970:993'>恭厥極惡等事固已乖矣而又推廣言之曰妖曰孽曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='993:1016'>旤曰痾曰眚曰沴復援春秋及漢亊以實之以瞽史矯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1016:1039'>誣之説亂彛倫攸叙之經害一也洛書之本文具在洪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1039:1065'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0054', 'WYG', '000-3b' );" name="000-3b" class="pb">[000-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1065:1088'>範劉歆之言非妄而宋儒乃創為白黒之點方圖之體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1088:1111'>九十之位則書也而變為圖矣且謂範之理可通於易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1111:1135'>故劉牧易數鉤𨼆以九位為河圖十位為洛書而蔡元</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1135:1158'>定兩易其名害二也洪範元無錯簡而宋儒任意改竄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1158:1181'>移庶徴王省惟嵗以下為五紀之傳移皇極斂時五福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1181:1204'>至其作汝用咎及三德惟辟作福以下並為五福六極</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1204:1227'>之傳害三矣愚為是解非敢撥棄舊詁而逞吾臆見也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1227:1250'>去其不正者以就其正者而聖人之意得矣自甲申迄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1250:1276'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0054', 'WYG', '000-4a' );" name="000-4a" class="pb">[000-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1276:1299'>己丑芟緐補闕辨誤析疑纂成五卷名之曰洪範正論</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1299:1305'>徳清胡渭</span><br/>
</p>
